        "subject": "LU-1147 llite: Reduce CPU overhead on larger striped files",
        "message": "LU-1147 llite: Reduce CPU overhead on larger striped files\n\nThe current read implementation in 1.8 results in an excessive\nnumber of calls to ll_readahead->obd_merge_lvb which will\nthen call lov_stripe_size for every stripe in a file.  As stripe\ncount increases this overhead begins to reduce read performance\non uncached files.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeremy Filizetti <jeremy.filizetti@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: Ie5343fe7936506030f6b470fd2de64ba36c25a6a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
